data.description:
NEW ROOF AND UPDATES INSIDE! PRICED TO SELL! SELLER SELLING AS IS!

Stunning 2-Story Beauty on a Tranquil Cul-de-Sac Lot!

Prepare to be wowed by this remarkable two-story gem nestled on a spacious cul-de-sac lot. Every detail is perfection, with a brand-new driveway and fresh paint ensuring stunning curb appeal. Entertain in style with wires and plugs thoughtfully prepped for a projector in the living area, taking movie nights to a whole new level!

With an extra-large garage, you'll have room for all your toys and more. This home is situated in an amazing neighborhood that boasts a serene, quiet ambiance, with minimal traffic passing through. You'll love the peacefulness that comes with it.

You'll appreciate the convenience of this home being within easy walking distance to school. The unique floor plan offers an array of options for customization and personalization, and there's no shortage of storage space for all your treasures. The downstairs powder room provides ultimate convenience for guests and visitors alike.

But that's not all – the possibilities are endless! Create multiple pantries to organize your kitchen to perfection. This home is a canvas waiting for your creative touch.

This is your chance to own a piece of quiet, suburban paradise on a pristine cul-de-sac lot. From a new driveway to the inviting living area, the exceptional location, and ample storage options, this home has it all. Don't wait; opportunities like this don't come around often! Great for investors!
